Hi Peter,

I think if you normalize your data (e.g., in the range [-1,1]), you can 
certainly give it a shot. You need to be careful about overfitting to 
your data, especially when all you have is daily data. Also, you need to 
be cautious about the fact that you&#39;d be trading a black box.

Sounds like a fun project though, best of luck!

Wesley

